# Computer Graphics

## ModelMoving
### 1. Requirements
OpenGl(freeglut3)
### 2. Usage 
+ array : zoom and rotate camera
+  w a s d q e : Move objects
+  c : change object to move 
+  t : switch between rendering faces and not
Move models demo.
